Hello I'm trying to get FAST_JIT working in a test CMake project, but have run into various errors trying to get it to build on linux x86_64 ubuntu LTS

Is there an example project using FAST_JIT I can examine?
Or is there a prebuilt library with FAST_JIT enabled somewhere - it looks like the releases on Github don't have FastJIT enabled.
There is no specific example for FAST_JIT only because there should be no extra installation or configuration for FAST_JIT. Would u mind sharing various errors messages and let's see what is going on
